data.description: Welcome home to this move in ready 3-bedroom 2.5 bath townhome located in the Villas at Woodsmere community, a quiet and well maintained community with LOW HOA!  As you enter through the foyer you will find a semi-open floorplan with lots of natural light.   The kitchen opens to the living/dining area and features stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, solid wood cabinets and plenty of countertop space to work with. Off the dining/living room are the sliding doors leading to the private patio with a storage closet and access to the green space.  All bedrooms and the laundry closet are located upstairs. The primary bedroom features a walk in closet and private shower tub combo with dual vanity sinks.  The community offers a resort style volleyball court and BBQ area. Conveniently located within minutes from numerous shopping and dining options, and with easy access to main thoroughfares, the townhome is not to miss! Schedule your private showing today!
